    "xml": "#$%送圆周率！（3.141592653589793860646274358622259488658754416659764815794568457485461146447545164879492584165497542138454215464664644212154875451234343434444969155675215541015210115601645897155151215647991758184911071015451458798154519781051……）\nfrom random import *\nfrom time import *\na = input(\"输入账号：\")\nb = input(\"输入密码：\")\nc = input(\"输入手机号：\")\nif len(c) != 11:\n    print(\"\\033[1;31m你是坏人！110！\")\n    for i in range(3):\n        print(\"\\033[2J\",end=\"\")\n        print(\"\\033[100A\",end=\"\")\n        print(\"\\033[1;33m代码运行结束\")\n        sleep(1-0.5)\n    while True:\n        print(\"\\033[2J\",end=\"\")\n        print(\"\\033[100A\",end=\"\")\n        print(\"\\033[1;31m电脑已出故障！\")\n        sleep(0.01)\nfor y in range(1):\n    print(\" _______________________\")\n    print(\"|                       |\")\n    print(\"|        登陆中……       |\")\n    print(\"|>----------------------|\")\n    print(\"|                       |\")\n    print(\" ———————————————————————\")\n    sleep(0.7)\n    print(\"\\033[2J\",end=\"\")\n    print(\"\\033[100A\",end=\"\")\n    print(\" _______________________\")\n    print(\"|                       |\")\n    print(\"|        登陆中……       |\")\n    print(\"|------------->---------|\")\n    print(\"|                       |\")\n    print(\" ———————————————————————\")\n    sleep(0.8)\n    print(\"\\033[2J\",end=\"\")\n    print(\"\\033[100A\",end=\"\")\n    print(\" _______________________\")\n    print(\"|                       |\")\n    print(\"|        登陆中……       |\")\n    print(\"|--------------------->-|\")\n    print(\"|                       |\")\n    print(\" ———————————————————————\")\n    sleep(0.8)\n    print(\"\\033[2J\",end=\"\")\n    print(\"\\033[100A\",end=\"\")\n    print(\"(\\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[0m)                    )\")\n    sleep(1.5)\n    print(\"\\033[2J\",end=\"\")\n    print(\"\\033[100A\",end=\"\")\n    print(\"(\\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[42m \\033[46m \\033[0m)\")\ndef fun(line):\n    for i in range(len(line)):\n        print(\"\\r\"+line[0:i+1],end=\"\")\n        sleep(0.1)\n    print()\nfun(\"解锁吧！\")\na_jie = input(\"\\033[1;33m手机号是：\")\nb_jie = input(\"\\033[1;33m密码是：\")\nc_jie = input(\"\\033[1;33m账号是：\")\nif a == c_jie and b == b_jie and c == a_jie:\n    print(c[0:4],\"***\",c[7:11],\"欢迎！\")\nelse :\n    print(\"\\033[41m错！\")\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
